--- Elizabeth Chase <lizzirrd@...> wrote:

>
> Oh, I know that, Deputy. I'm just having fun. You
> didn't even gig me on my mis-spelling. *pout*

I handle chronic cases--everyone's entitled to one
mistake. Ein Only! Vee have vays of making du shpell!
Shpell! Shpell Shpell!


> So. Which generation of stormtrooper armor do you
> wear ..... or did you snip it all up and make
> lamellar armor following the Way of
> the Barrel? (Some SCA players use the large plastic
> barrels ---- preferably previously unused.)

Nothing so science-fiction. How could I rag on anime
geeks in good conscience then?

messages.messageBody:
Oh, I know that, Deputy. I'm just having fun. You didn't even gig me on my mis-spelling. *pout*

So. Which generation of stormtrooper armor do you wear ..... or did you snip it all up and make lamellar armor following the Way of
the Barrel? (Some SCA players use the large plastic barrels ---- preferably previously unused.)

Silly Girl
--- who wants to stay up late tonight and watch 'Hero' after her young bushi are strapped in their beds for the night.
